* Located in the popular Závodie district of Žilina, within walking distance to the city center.

* Relaxing spots nearby: Rajčanka riverbank, Hájik or Hradisko mountain hikes.
* Public transport stop right next to the building.

**Parking:**
* Dedicated parking space in front of the apartment.
* Largest garage available for an additional fee.

**Apartment Features:**
* Ground floor apartment with a heated parking space underneath.
* Secure entrance with soundproof and fire-resistant doors.
* Only one neighbor above.
* Spacious living area (28.88 m2) with a U-shaped kitchen unit equipped with appliances.
* Open plan living/dining area with built-in wardrobe and pantry.
* Bathroom with shower enclosure, bathtub, sink, mirror, electric towel dryer.
* Additional room that can be used as a second bathroom, wardrobe, or sauna.
* Two bedrooms (15.38 m2 and 15.93 m2) with built-in wardrobes and southeast orientation for morning sun.
* West-facing living area for afternoon sunlight.
* Cellar (2.4 m2).

* Apartment has been serviced prior to sale.
* Financing available up to 100% of the purchase price through a mortgage with an interest rate starting at 3.95%.",
